HEADWORD: Inconsequential
<hw>In*con`se*quen"tial</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not
regularly following from the premises; hence, irrelevant; unimportant;
of no consequence.</def> <au>Chesterfield.</au> --
<wordforms><wf>In*con`se*quen"tial*ly</wf> <pr>(#)</pr>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inconsequentiality</ent>⟦br⟧
